WEBVTT

01:33.051 --> 01:36.471
<b>Genki Trading</b>

01:35.301 --> 01:36.471
<b>Check this out, Sasaki.</b>

01:36.761 --> 01:40.471
<b>Apparently, the brand of cigarettes 
someone smokes says a lot about them.</b>

01:41.431 --> 01:42.731
<b>What's this about?</b>

01:44.441 --> 01:46.401
<b>It's the smoke brand personality test.</b>

01:46.401 --> 01:50.611
<b>This stuff really gets the young'uns 
going during drinking parties.</b>

01:50.611 --> 01:52.241
<b>What does it say about me?</b>

01:52.821 --> 01:57.241
<b>"Straightforward and devoted, 
will never cheat," it says!</b>

01:59.241 --> 02:03.501
<b>It also says, 
"Oblivious and socially inept."</b>

02:03.501 --> 02:08.131
<b>Hey! You didn't have to read that part!</b>

02:08.131 --> 02:09.421
<b>Read the room!</b>

02:09.421 --> 02:13.341
<b>Are you listening to me 
or not? Which is it?</b>

02:12.261 --> 02:15.181
<b><i>A popular topic among the youth, huh?</i></b>

02:14.261 --> 02:15.181
<b>Why are you smiling now?</b>

02:22.681 --> 02:25.561
<b>Oh, yeah, that stuff.</b>

02:25.561 --> 02:28.021
<b>You knew about it?</b>

02:28.021 --> 02:29.571
<b>Just that it exists.</b>

02:29.571 --> 02:32.861
<b>But those things usually...</b>

02:32.861 --> 02:34.321
<b>A coworker told me about it,</b>

02:34.701 --> 02:37.111
<b>and I thought it sounded fun.</b>

02:35.361 --> 02:37.281
<b>Best</b>

02:35.361 --> 02:37.281
<b>Intentions</b>

02:39.701 --> 02:41.951
<b>A'ight, let's check it out.</b>

02:43.081 --> 02:45.251
<b>What's it say about you, Sasaki-san?</b>

02:45.711 --> 02:50.591
<b>Erm... there it is. It says...</b>

02:51.381 --> 02:55.261
<b>"Tends to be a masochist despite 
otherwise looking down on others."</b>

02:56.591 --> 02:57.971
<b>What in the world?</b>

02:57.971 --> 03:00.931
<b>Stop that... Let me smoke.</b>

03:00.931 --> 03:01.851
<b>For real.</b>

03:02.811 --> 03:05.681
<b>Wh-What was your result?</b>

03:08.521 --> 03:12.071
<b>"Two-faced, with a surprisingly 
high sex drive."</b>

03:13.981 --> 03:18.451
<b>These things usually bring up 
sex stuff as a punchline.</b>

03:18.451 --> 03:21.701
<b>And you can see right through 
the creator's prejudices.</b>

03:23.791 --> 03:27.161
<b><i>Funny how it was totally right 
about one thing, though.</i></b>

03:24.371 --> 03:27.621
<b>Dark</b>

03:24.371 --> 03:27.621
<b>Light</b>

03:30.961 --> 03:32.671
<b>I apologize.</b>

03:34.341 --> 03:36.801
<b>Huh? What are you kneeling for?</b>

03:37.131 --> 03:39.391
<b>Where'd your cigarette and glasses go?</b>

03:40.931 --> 03:46.681
<b>I'm really sorry for unknowingly 
bringing up such an awkward topic...</b>

03:47.481 --> 03:49.101
<b>and for making you say that out loud.</b>

03:55.361 --> 03:56.401
<b>I mean,</b>

03:56.401 --> 03:59.861
<b>yeah, I <i>do</i> hate dirty talk.</b>

03:59.201 --> 04:00.531
<b>Hates dirty talk</b>

04:00.951 --> 04:05.331
<b>But I know you only brought it up 
thinking the youth found it fun.</b>

04:08.791 --> 04:12.171
<b>You did it for me but ended up 
apologizing for it anyway.</b>

04:13.881 --> 04:15.801
<b>Way to make yourself 
look silly, Sasaki-san.</b>

04:20.681 --> 04:24.851
<b>I'm not mad at you, okay? 
Get back to smoking.</b>

04:24.851 --> 04:26.061
<b>Tayama-san...</b>

04:26.391 --> 04:29.731
<b>It might actually be right 
about you being two-faced.</b>

04:31.311 --> 04:35.441
<b>I've been thinking it for a while, 
but I had trouble putting it into words.</b>

04:36.071 --> 04:37.941
<b>But I get it now.</b>

04:41.821 --> 04:44.201
<b>You act all aloof, but you're really nice!</b>

04:44.201 --> 04:46.911
<b>That's exactly the kind of person you are!</b>

04:55.541 --> 04:56.711
<b>Tayama-san?</b>

04:58.171 --> 05:00.971
<b>You were about to smoke 
that one earlier, right?</b>

05:00.971 --> 05:03.471
<b>Oh, yeah, thanks?</b>

05:03.841 --> 05:05.851
<b>Right, sorry.</b>

05:05.851 --> 05:07.601
<b>I completely forgot.</b>

05:08.271 --> 05:10.351
<b>Want me to light it for you, too?</b>

05:13.021 --> 05:15.731
<b>D-Did I do something to make you mad?</b>

05:15.731 --> 05:18.651
<b>I'm not mad. Just look 
at my thousand-watt smile.</b>

05:29.951 --> 05:32.331
<b>L-Let me say I'm sorry anyway.</b>

05:32.331 --> 05:33.581
<b>What're you apologizing for?</b>

05:36.381 --> 05:38.881
<b>24-Hour</b>

05:36.381 --> 05:38.881
<b>Supermarket S</b>

05:38.881 --> 05:40.511
<b>Yummy Mochi Chips</b>

05:43.431 --> 05:48.761
<b><i>In the end, I just left after making 
Tayama-san upset last night.</i></b>

05:51.601 --> 05:53.141
<b>Thank you! Come again!</b>

05:56.151 --> 06:00.151
<b><i>Should a guy like me really be lining up 
at Yamada-san's register?</i></b>

06:00.781 --> 06:01.901
<b><i>No way.</i></b>

06:05.071 --> 06:06.531
<b>Sir.</b>

06:07.031 --> 06:10.541
<b>Please step this way. 
I can ring you up now.</b>

06:10.831 --> 06:12.541
<b>R-Right.</b>

06:27.471 --> 06:28.301
<b>Oh?</b>

06:30.681 --> 06:33.731
<b><i>Something funny happened 
between those two, huh?</i></b>

06:33.731 --> 06:35.391
<b><i>Wish I could've seen it.</i></b>

07:00.791 --> 07:01.591
<b>Man...</b>

07:02.001 --> 07:05.921
<b>We're sorry for making you 
come all the way in this heat.</b>

07:05.921 --> 07:08.301
<b>Oh, don't mention it.</b>

07:08.301 --> 07:10.181
<b>Please have this tea.</b>

07:12.261 --> 07:13.521
<b>I'll do just that.</b>

07:13.521 --> 07:14.641
<b>Go for it.</b>

07:18.771 --> 07:23.651
<b>The proposal you sent over 
really helped us out.</b>

07:23.651 --> 07:28.241
<b>Our owner was over the moon, saying, 
"You can always count on Genki Trading!"</b>

07:28.491 --> 07:29.871
<b>I'm glad to hear it.</b>

07:29.871 --> 07:31.411
<b><i>Good afternoon, everyone.</i></b>

07:31.411 --> 07:35.331
<b><i>We've had a string of summer-like 
days since the start of May.</i></b>

07:36.251 --> 07:39.371
<b>We've already switched over 
to business casual.</b>

07:39.671 --> 07:42.421
<b>That's wonderful.</b>

07:42.421 --> 07:45.881
<b>We aren't allowed to 
until summer's actually here.</b>

07:46.631 --> 07:48.511
<b>That sounds rough.</b>

07:48.511 --> 07:51.011
<b>Nationwide Forecast</b>

07:48.971 --> 07:51.011
<b><i>In northern Japan, 
the entirety of tomorrow...</i></b>

07:51.011 --> 07:53.931
<b>Anyway, we're counting on you.</b>

07:53.931 --> 07:55.271
<b>Thank you very much.</b>

07:55.971 --> 07:58.641
<b>What's next on your schedule? 
Back to the office for more work?</b>

07:58.641 --> 08:01.101
<b>No, I think I can head 
straight home today.</b>

08:01.101 --> 08:02.941
<b>Glad to hear it.</b>

08:02.941 --> 08:05.441
<b>You're always working 
much too hard, Sasaki-san.</b>

08:33.641 --> 08:37.981
<b><i>I can't deal with how warm it is 
all the way until evening.</i></b>

08:38.481 --> 08:41.901
<b><i>If it's like this already, how much 
worse is summer going to get?</i></b>

08:49.401 --> 08:51.071
<b>That ice cream's good, huh?</b>

08:51.741 --> 08:52.661
<b>Yep!</b>

08:53.121 --> 08:55.121
<b>You did sweat a lot.</b>

08:55.121 --> 08:55.911
<b>So hot.</b>

08:55.911 --> 08:59.121
<b><i>Maybe I'll get some ice cream 
for the walk home.</i></b>

08:59.121 --> 09:01.621
<b>24-Hour</b>

08:59.121 --> 09:01.621
<b>Supermarket S</b>

09:06.001 --> 09:09.091
<b><i>Of course it'd be crowded at this time.</i></b>

09:10.131 --> 09:11.631
<b><i>Wait, what?</i></b>

09:12.971 --> 09:15.141
<b><i>Y-Yamada-san?!</i></b>

09:16.561 --> 09:19.431
<b><i>She's working the evening shift today?</i></b>

09:19.431 --> 09:21.691
<b><i>What a lucky day!</i></b>

09:21.691 --> 09:23.061
<b>Thank you for shopping with us!</b>

09:25.401 --> 09:27.861
<b><i>H-H-H-Half sleeves?!</i></b>

09:27.861 --> 09:29.781
<b>I'll just update your point card.</b>

09:30.401 --> 09:33.321
<b><i>Oh, so they switched 
to the summer uniform!</i></b>

09:33.321 --> 09:35.911
<b><i>Such a refreshing look!</i></b>

09:36.701 --> 09:38.911
<b><i>And heck, Yamada-san's just so...</i></b>

09:39.201 --> 09:40.451
<b><i>so pr...</i></b>

09:43.621 --> 09:46.001
<b><i>Guess I don't need that ice cream anymore.</i></b>

09:46.001 --> 09:47.211
<b><i>I'll just go.</i></b>

09:53.721 --> 09:56.721
<b>Ice Cream Bar</b>

09:56.721 --> 10:00.721
<b>You left without shopping yesterday 
even though Yamada-san was there.</b>

10:01.391 --> 10:02.351
<b>Why?</b>

10:06.061 --> 10:08.071
<b>Were you watching again?</b>

10:08.071 --> 10:12.111
<b>Who wouldn't notice a tall dude 
hanging around the entrance?</b>

10:12.111 --> 10:14.861
<b>Oh, sorry. Was I a bother?</b>

10:16.241 --> 10:18.371
<b>So, why'd you do it?</b>

10:22.541 --> 10:26.581
<b>It was so hot yesterday, 
I started craving some ice cream.</b>

10:26.581 --> 10:27.631
<b>Yeah?</b>

10:28.341 --> 10:32.671
<b>But the store was such a low-cortisol 
zone that it cooled me down plenty.</b>

10:32.671 --> 10:34.341
<b>What does that even mean?</b>

10:36.891 --> 10:42.391
<b>And here I thought the sight of Yamada-san
in short sleeves blew the heat away.</b>

10:43.681 --> 10:46.061
<b>Ow! Hot!</b>

10:46.311 --> 10:48.021
<b>Bingo, huh?</b>

10:48.021 --> 10:49.561
<b>No, no, not at all!</b>

10:52.781 --> 10:57.701
<b>Retail workers like Yamada-san switch 
uniforms to herald the changing seasons.</b>

10:57.701 --> 10:59.241
<b>All I have for them is gratitude—</b>

10:59.241 --> 11:01.331
<b>You didn't find it pretty, then?</b>

11:01.331 --> 11:02.581
<b>I did not say that!</b>

11:12.301 --> 11:16.131
<b>I do believe short sleeves 
suit her very well.</b>

11:17.131 --> 11:19.431
<b>You're sweating buckets.</b>

11:19.431 --> 11:21.471
<b>I mean, it's pretty hot today.</b>

11:23.391 --> 11:24.641
<b>Huh...</b>

11:25.601 --> 11:28.941
<b>Aren't you hot in that jacket?</b>

11:28.941 --> 11:32.981
<b>I'm dressed lightly underneath. 
Nothing compared to you.</b>

11:32.981 --> 11:34.991
<b>Oh, you are?</b>

11:35.241 --> 11:36.071
<b>Yeah.</b>

11:38.451 --> 11:39.241
<b>Check it out.</b>

11:41.201 --> 11:42.991
<b>T-Tayama-san, uh...</b>

11:42.991 --> 11:44.121
<b>I'm sorry.</b>

11:46.621 --> 11:49.001
<b>I'm sorry for looking at your belly!</b>

11:49.541 --> 11:50.791
<b>You know...</b>

11:54.381 --> 11:56.381
<b>Doesn't your belly feel cold like that?</b>

11:59.431 --> 12:00.971
<b><i>Doesn't your belly feel cold like that?</i></b>

12:00.971 --> 12:02.471
<b><i>Doesn't your belly feel cold like that?</i></b>

12:02.471 --> 12:03.391
<b><i>...like that?</i></b>

12:03.391 --> 12:04.221
<b><i>...like that?</i></b>

12:04.221 --> 12:05.641
<b><i>...that? ...that? ...that?</i></b>

12:05.641 --> 12:09.271
<b></b>Yamada's Short Sleeves

12:07.561 --> 12:09.271
<b><i>How wonderful!</i></b>

12:09.271 --> 12:14.021
<b></b>Tayama's Belly

12:09.561 --> 12:10.851
<b><i>Yay.</i></b>

12:11.401 --> 12:13.651
<b><i>Aren't you cold? Are you sure about this?</i></b>

12:19.401 --> 12:22.371
<b><i>I swear, this geezer...</i></b>

12:24.531 --> 12:25.491
<b>Tayama-san?</b>

12:26.581 --> 12:28.001
<b>Use this if you'd like.</b>

12:28.871 --> 12:31.041
<b>The night breeze still gets chilly.</b>

12:35.381 --> 12:38.881
<b>Oh, if you'd rather not, that's fine.</b>

12:38.881 --> 12:39.801
<b>Huh?</b>

12:40.431 --> 12:44.761
<b>Sorry, Tayama-san, I meant 
to use it to cover your belly.</b>

12:44.761 --> 12:46.891
<b>I wasn't telling you to wear it!</b>

12:46.891 --> 12:48.431
<b>That'd make you uncomfortable...</b>

12:49.311 --> 12:49.811
<b>Wouldn't it?</b>

12:52.811 --> 12:55.111
<b>Uh, Tayama-san?</b>

13:02.321 --> 13:04.571
<b>Shut it, arm man.</b>

13:04.571 --> 13:06.581
<b>A-Arm man...?</b>

13:08.121 --> 13:08.911
<b>Blep.</b>

13:13.501 --> 13:16.881
<b><i>I don't get it. What does 
she mean, "arm man"?</i></b>

13:29.471 --> 13:33.981
<b><i>This must be what makes me dense.</i></b>

13:43.321 --> 13:47.581
<b><i>Sasaki likes arms more than 
he does bellies, huh?</i></b>

13:49.411 --> 13:51.371
<b></b>flab

13:54.171 --> 13:57.211
<b>I should lay off the ramen for a while.</b>

14:01.251 --> 14:04.881
<b>Translation: Sriram Gurunathan</b>

14:05.381 --> 14:09.011
<b>Editing & Typesetting: Geoff Mazzolini
Subtitle Timing: Krzysztof Kunc</b>

14:09.721 --> 14:12.971
<b>Quality Check: Zachary Carlysle
Translation Check: Sho Stifler</b>
